## Minecraft Bedrock

Download BedrockTogether [BedrockTogether](https://bedrocktogether.net/) on your phone.

Start the Bedrock Together app, where you will see Connect and an area to enter the IP and Port of the server.

Enter your server's IP and Port into these fields.

Then click the Run button to start the app, and it'll work to route the connection to your Xbox.

Open Minecraft on your console and navigate to the Friends tab and then locate the LAN section. The server should be displayed here.

You can now select the server to begin connecting. Once you're connected, you can then close the Bedrock Together app.
